-- Limited posts 8 percent drop in Jan same-store sales
-- 
-- Thu Feb 7, 2008 7:51am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/02/07/us-usa-retailsales-limited-idUSWNAS983220080207

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Limited Brands Inc ( LTD.N ) said on Thursday that sales at established stores fell 8 percent in January. 

 The operator of the Victoria's Secret and Bath & Body Works chains said that total sales fell to $625.8 million for the four weeks ended February 2, from $1.06 billion for the five weeks ended February 3, 2007. Analysts, on average, had been expecting the retailer to post a same-store sales decline of 7.2 percent. (Reporting by  Aarthi Sivaraman ; Editing by Steve Orlofsky)